column1: These data are consistent with data reported to CDC for Abortion Surveillance -- United States, 2020 found at: https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/71/ss/ss7110a1.htm?s_cid=ss7110a1_w
"--"  Reporting area did not report, or data not reportable by CDC.

** Reporting area did not report, or only reported by occurrence; because abortion numbers by residence are available only from other reporting areas where residents obtained abortions, data by area of residence should be interpreted with caution.
